<plot>Journalist 'Geraldo Rivera' (qv) hosted this much-hyped live-on-TV opening of gangster Al Capone's secret vault beneath the Lexington Hotel in Chicago, Illinois, USA. After much fanfare, including the presence of a medical examiner in case human remains were discovered, the vault was revealed to contain... considerably less than many anticipated.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?578147</url></doc>
